headline: Bitcoin Prices Stand Near $88,000 as Volatile Week Nears End
summary: Bitcoin held broadly steady Friday, after a volatile stretch in which the digital currency set a series of new highs. The largest cryptocurrency by market value recently traded at about $87,892, up less than 0.
